['<blockquote>','1 Tim 4:1-2&mdash;Now the Spirit speaketh expressly&#44; that in the latter times some shall depart from the faith&#44; giving heed to seducing spirits&#44; and doctrines of devils; 2) Speaking lies in hypocrisy; having their conscience seared with a hot iron; ','I Timotheo 4:1-2&mdash;Basi roho anena wazi wazi ya kwamba nyakati za mwisho wengine watajitenga na imani wakisikiliza roho zidanganyao&#44; na mafundisho ye mashetani; 2) Kwa urafiki wa watu wasemauo uongo&#44; wakichamwa moto dhamiri zao wenyewe. ','</blockquote>'],
