['<blockquote>','Rev. 16:10&mdash;…his kingdom was full of darkness; and they gnawed their tongues for pain&#44;','Ufunuo 16:10&mdash;… Ufalme wake ukatiwa gizi; wakatafuna ndimi zao kw sabau ya maumivu.','</blockquote>'],
['<h2>','They are spiritually immature.','Siyo watu wazima kirohoni.','</h2>'],
